359
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:51,680
General Tangchuan Anfu suggests

360
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:53,080
that you take this plane.

361
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,320
The women accompanying you

362
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:58,280
can travel to the island by boat first.

363
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:02,160
Regarding this sudden change,

364
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:04,640
Wumu used the opportunity of checking the schedule

365
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:07,600
to quickly weigh the pros and cons of this development.

366
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:08,200
Suddenly,

367
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:09,240
he realized

368
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:11,160
he couldn't refuse this arrangement.

369
